  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Roll out the flaky pastry and place in a 9x13 inch baking dish.",
    "Brown the smoked sausage in a pan over medium heat.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix together the crumble topping, cheese, eggs, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the browned sausage to the crumble mixture and stir until combined.",
